data.description: The Madison Plan built by My Home Communities. This community is just a short drive to Atlanta Motor Speedway. This beautiful spacious Ranch Plan with a view to a Large Family Room features a Large Kitchen with Island,Granite Countertops,36" Shaker Cabinets with Crown Trim, Backsplash, Stainless Steel Appliances,Dining Room with Wainscotting, Large Primary with Spacious Closet, Double Vanity,Shower with framed door, Super Tile in Primary Shower,Spacious Closet, Granite Countertops in All Baths, Wideplank LVP Flooring,Covered Patio, Garage Door Opener with 2 Remotes. Seller will contribute up to $7,000 in closing cost. Home will be ready in 2023.
